OL,6,G1800 Shetland: Scotland's Wondrous
OL,7,G     Isles
OL,8,     FWith 1700 miles of coastline,
OL,9,     FShetland loves a race in a yoal: a
OL,10,     Ftraditional boat with links to the
OL,11,     FVikings. We meet a skipper
OL,12,     Fpreparing for the last race of the
OL,13,     Fseason. (Ep4)
OL,14,G1900 Tour de France 2026
OL,15,     FThe peloton travels from Hagetmau
OL,16,     Fto Bordeaux in Stage 7. The
